data.description: Fantastic home located in a wonderful cul-de-sac close to schools, Pembroke Center, Routes 27 and 36. This 3 bedroom, 2.5 bath home offers plenty of space throughout and is filled with natural light & bright with updated recessed lighting. The kitchen has beautiful granite countertops and a newer backsplash with a great floor plan for entertaining and relaxing. Hardwood floors and ceramic tile throughout the first floor and a cozy fire-placed living room is very inviting. You will find first floor laundry tucked away next to the powder room. The second floor offers 3 bedroom, 2 full baths, and a home office. The master bedroom offers a vaulted ceiling and a spacious en-suite bathroom and walk in closet. There is bonus finished space in the basement, let your imagination create this space to fit your needs! This home sits on approximately 40,000 square feet. Best & Highest Due by April 18, 2024 at 12:00 Noon.
